  "instructions": [
    "Combine bean sprouts with tandoori seasoning in a large bowl.",
    "Add garlic, lemon zest, sun-dried tomatoes, red onion, parsley, feta cheese, almonds, and chickpeas. Mix well.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the mixture and toss until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Serve chilled as a side dish or on top of toast for a delicious brunch treat."
